#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:1965
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:2043
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:793
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1352
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1745
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2056
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1992
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1443
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:1204
msgid "Unfortunately, not."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vygwynyc
#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [message], speaker=Aenyc
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:1969
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:2047
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:797
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1749
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2060
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1996
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1447
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:1208
msgid "Come back when you do then."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2000
msgid "You look injured. What happened to you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2004
msgid ""
"Sorry for not being very presentable. I got hit by an arrow last night but "
"it's only a scratch."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2008
msgid "But I'm ready to go back to the fight, if someone finally believes in me."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2023
msgid "I'm Is, the bowwoman. If your need a good bowman, don't look further."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2038
msgid "Gaelyn fixed me after I was injured defending the village."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2049
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1597
msgid "Can we help you with something?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2057
msgid ""
"I need 525 gold to pay Gaelyn. If you help me with that, I will come fight "
"with you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2061
msgid "Are you interested?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2063
msgid "Sure, here is the gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2088
msgid ""
"At your service. Just tell me where we go, and I will do what I can so that "
"we arrive there alive."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2101
msgid ""
"Is is a hero. Heroes, of whom you will soon have a collection, will always be"
" recalled automatically. Heroes can pick up and equip items. Once recruited, "
"they will provide you with an additional unit type to recruit. If a hero "
"dies, you won't be able to recruit this unit type anymore."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2107
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1907
msgid "You can now recruit bowmen."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2113
msgid ""
"I appreciate the trust you place in me, but I need to pay my debts before "
"everything. Come back when you have the gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2124
msgid "You never know, right? If you change your mind, you know where to find me."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2181
msgid ""
"The divine fire is in you, my child. Your destiny might incline you to "
"accomplish great things, but let's begin by dealing with the most urgent "
"matters first."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2196
msgid ""
"If you need potions, I can sell you useful ones and at low price. Do you want"
" to see them?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2198
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1340
