#. [message], speaker=Marogin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2336
msgid ""
"If you go north, know that only orcs come back from this direction since last"
" night's attack. If you wipe out the scum prowling around Qyizu's pass, it "
"will be far easier for us to make the road safe when the captain will order "
"us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2371
msgid ""
"I think we are done with Zei. I would rather go back to the Arable Highlands,"
" but the kingdom needs us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2387
msgid "We don't have enough food to continue our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2404
msgid "We don't have anything to transport our food."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\06_Zei.cfg:2430
msgid "The inhabitants should be able to fish now."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=07_Yooradweak_s_pass
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:4
msgid "Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:43
msgid "Get to the other side of Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:59
msgid "Clear Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:75
msgid "Find another way to Udxatfe"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:97
msgid "Find the entrance of Uvju's cross"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:126
msgid "Free the northern watchtower before completing the main objective"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:361
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:375
msgid ""
"Our next stop is Udxatfe. We need to tell the guardian about what happened "
"here in Zei."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:365
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:379
msgid ""
"He will surely be able to draw more information with his knowledge than we "
"with ours."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:369
msgid ""
"The shortest way is to go west through Yooradweak's pass then through Qyizu's"
" mines"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:383
msgid "From what I know, the shortest way is to go west through Yooradweak's pass."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:396
msgid ""
"We must expect to encounter orcish resistance there. Clearing the pass will "
"benefit us but also the people of Zei."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:413
msgid "Uvju's cross"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:431
msgid ""
"The pass is on the other side of the bridge. The tower you see south is Zei's"
" northern watchtower."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:448
msgid ""
"North: Uvju's cross\n"
"West: Zei\n"
"East: Qyizu, Udxatfe"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:479
msgid "I think we found the northern watchtower."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:485
msgid "A lot of men have died here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:489
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:831
msgid "There is a lever on the floor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:499
msgid ""
"It might be the way to open the arsenal. I hope the orcs haven't found it "
"first."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:505
msgid "Should I pull it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:572
msgid "The arsenal is opened. Alas it looks like the orcs are already in."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:578
msgid "It opened a secret passage."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:602
msgid "The doors are closed. Let's try to open them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:621
msgid ""
"I can't open it. It looks like someone has stacked rocks on the other side of"
" the door."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:625
msgid "I don't know if orcs or humans did it, but we can't use the pass."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:629
msgid "We need to find another way to reach Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:639
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:662
msgid "There is a way."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:643
msgid ""
"A tunnel runs through the mountain. It begins in Uvju's cross and end on the "
"other side of the pass."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:647
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:670
msgid "But this is a dark way, full of horrors from the War of Legions."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:651
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:674
msgid "We don't have much choice. We must carry the message to Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:666
msgid ""
"I've read that a tunnel run through the mountain. It begins in Uvju's cross "
"and end on the other side of the pass."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:694
msgid "I’m glad to see another human."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:704
msgid "Who are you, soldier?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:716
msgid ""
"My troops and I tried to flee from the orcs when they invaded Qyizu, but "
"Zei’s road being blocked, our only option was to go through Uvju’s cross."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:720
msgid "This is not..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:724
msgid ""
"What a monumental mistake we made there. We had made half the way when those "
"eight-legged monsters began coming in bulk out of the tunnels."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:728
msgid "We took to our heels, but… "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:732
msgid "But… "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:736
msgid "But what?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:740
msgid "My God! How deafening were their screams."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:744
msgid "Why does this happen to me? Why?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:748
msgid ""
"I don't think we will get more info from him. What happened in there seems to"
" have broken his mind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:772
msgid "I think I found Aldrsil's axe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:807
msgid ""
"If we had any other choice, I would rather us not have to pass through Uvju's"
" cross, especially after what Ofcuu told us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:811
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, the pass is blocked, and we have to warn the guardian of "
"Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:815
msgid "Let's enter the tunnels but be careful everyone."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:834
msgid "Hello there. Do you intend to go inside Uvju's cross?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#. [1]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:838
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:435
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:449
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:842
msgid ""
"At this time of year, at this time of day, in this part of the country, "
"without a healer?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:846
#: .\utils\help.cfg:19
msgid "Yes."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:850
msgid "...May I see that?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:854
msgid "...No."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:858
msgid ""
"You know what? I will come anyway.\n"
"Leaving you enter the cross without a healer would be like killing you "
"myself."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:863
msgid ""
"But take note that I will not fight for you and will leave when we arrive in "
"Qyizu."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:867
msgid "But we did not ask for your help."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:871
msgid "Come on! Let's go!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:925
msgid ""
"There are too many orcs between us and Udxatfe. How are we supposed to get "
"there?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:943
msgid ""
"The pass is blocked. There is no way we will be able to reach Udxatfe and "
"warn the guardian."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:961
msgid ""
"If trained men weren't able to go through Uvju's cross, how could we? We are "
"barely able to kill some orcs."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:4
msgid "Inside Uvju's Cross"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:40
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:33
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:41
msgid "Find the exit of Uvju's cross"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:45
msgid "Defeat the enemy leader before exiting"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Monstrosity LotI
#. [side], type=Skeleton Archer
#. [side], type=Ghast
#. [side], type=Draug
#. [side], type=Ancient Lich
#. [side], type=Deathlord LotI
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:100
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:82
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:89
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1237
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\36_Old_Temple_Road.cfg:337
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\37_Old_Temple.cfg:83
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\38_Isut.cfg:116
msgid "Undead"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Spiderling LoI
#. [side], type=Young Giant Spider LoI
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:439
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:273
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:401
msgid "Spiders"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:645
msgid "So, here is the famous Uvju's cross."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:649
msgid "Well, it doesn't look nice anyway. Even without what Ofcuu told us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:653
msgid ""
"However, it is the only way to reach Qyizu now that Yooradweak's pass is "
"blocked. I hope no one is afraid of spiders because I can already hear them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:666
msgid ""
"This must be the spiders the demons left. It's impressive that they are still"
" here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:670
msgid "But not really reassuring."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:737
msgid "Yes, let's quit this corridor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:864
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:970
msgid "There are spiders coming out of the pits!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:893
msgid "I would love to study them were they not trying to kill us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:914
msgid "There are spiders coming out of the pits and traps!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1105
msgid "The books on the shelf are badly damaged."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1109
msgid "Wait! I found one that should be readable!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1128
msgid "Awesome! Give it to me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1150
msgid "There is more mold than paper on this shelf."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1154
msgid "It looks like one of the books has not been completely eaten by the mold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1173
msgid "Don't touch it! Let me treat it with the care it deserves."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1192
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:568
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:482
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:532
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:665
msgid "There are spiders coming out of the traps!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1269
msgid "A frightening lot of spiders!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1335
msgid "Damned orcs! It looks like they have raised undead here too."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1339
msgid "If we can find the undead leader and defeat it, it will be easier to exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1363
msgid "Come over here! I think I found something."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1383
msgid "It looks like an elevator. We could use it to go back to the surface."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1393
msgid "Except that I can't see any light when I look up."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1399
msgid "I don't think so... I can't see any light when I look up."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1405
msgid "I don't see any other path. We must take it and see where it leads to."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1427
msgid "Let's go down. I hope the exit is down there and spiders are not."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1455
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:846
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1050
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the spiders here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1472
msgid "This was one ugly undead. I am quite sure it was leading the others."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1476
msgid "It should be easier for us now that it is dead."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1484
msgid "My God! The screams! They are deafening!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1488
msgid "Why is this happening to us? Why?"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=09_Spider_Maze
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:4
msgid "Spider Maze"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:38
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:46
msgid "Kill all spiders"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:526
msgid ""
"I'm afraid we will have to deal with spiders down here too. Probably undead "
"also."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:539
msgid ""
"It would be a good thing if we were able to get rid of the spiders. That "
"would allow scholars to study that ruin."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:545
msgid ""
"It would be a good thing if we were able to get rid of the spiders. Not that "
"it would become a popular place, but still."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:551
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, I'm not sure we have the time to do this. Our main mission "
"remains to warn the guardian."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:690
msgid "There is a large rusty door. Should I try to open it?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:692
msgid "Yes, let's fight what's behind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:734
msgid ""
"There is a large iron door. It looks like there is a huge hall on the other "
"side of it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:738
msgid ""
"It would be better to close it back once we will have crossed so that no "
"spider tries to attack us from behind. Should I try to open the door now?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:781
msgid "There is a large wooden door. Should I open it"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:800
msgid "Caution! A spider was hiding on the ceiling."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:834
msgid ""
"We have not killed all the spiders before us, but the mission is more "
"important. Let's proceed to this new room."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:871
msgid "I think we killed all the spiders living in this part of Uvju's cross."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:875
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1079
msgid "It looks like this one was guarding a treasure."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:879
msgid ""
"Let's take it, we will need it for our journey. \n"
"Now, let's proceed to the next room."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:915
msgid "This place is a maze!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:919
msgid ""
"We spend too much time in there. And we don't even know for sure the exit "
"still exists."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:934
msgid "There is a zombi here."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:938
msgid "It looks... lost?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:942
msgid ""
"It might be what remains of a poor soul that got lost in this maze. Let's try"
" not to finish like that."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=10_Great_Hall
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:4
msgid "Great Hall"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:454
msgid "Wahoo! This room is huge! I'm pretty sure it must be nice to visit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:461
msgid "Or at least it would be if it wasn't full of spiders and undead."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:465
msgid "Let's find a way out. I'm getting really tired of all those spiders."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:582
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:628
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:785
msgid "Some spiders are born from this sack."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:766
msgid "A lot of spiders!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:863
msgid "It has closed the door."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:881
msgid "The door is open again."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:958
msgid ""
"I think I found another elevator! Let's see if this one goes back to the "
"surface."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:979
msgid ""
"This looks like a bigger version of the spiders. It must be their queen or "
"something like that."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:983
msgid ""
"I doubt that. Adult Giant Spiders are bigger than that. This must still be a "
"young one."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:987
msgid ""
"It might be commanding the ones that are attacking us, but there must be a "
"mother somewhere."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1008
msgid "Ah! There it is!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1012
msgid "This must be the mother. And it seems to be blocking the way."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1034
msgid "I can see the, sun up there. Hurrah!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1038
msgid "Let's go back up. We should arrive on the other side of Yooradweak's pass."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1075
msgid ""
"I think we killed all the remaining spiders of Uvju's cross. It should be "
"easier to cross for others now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1083
msgid "Let's take it, we will need it for our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1109
msgid "Are we going to see an infinite number of spiders?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1113
msgid ""
"Don't be stupid son. An infinite number of something does not exist. There "
"could be a lot of them though."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1117
msgid ""
"The good thing is they do not seem to arrive all at once. We simply need to "
"kill them faster than they arrive and move forward."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1121
msgid ""
"There has to be a finite number of spiders, because there is no infinite "
"source of food and those things need to eat."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1125
msgid ""
"There is probably a spider queen somewhere in there that is sending them at "
"us. If we manage to kill it, they should stop coming for us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1133
msgid "Too many spiders. Too many undead."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1137
msgid "This place is too huge. The exit could be anywhere."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1141
msgid "We won't get out of here alive."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1157
msgid "That's it. No more spiders should attack us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia,Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1161
msgid "Well yes, but actually no."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia,Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:1165
msgid ""
"It only means that spiders won't come looking for us anymore. But if we "
"disturb spiders that are there, they will attack us anyway."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:51
msgid "Save at least one dwarf"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:61
msgid "Talk to Amin"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:79
msgid "Talk to a dwarf"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:97
msgid "Enter the mine"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:112
msgid "Open the door of Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:112
msgid "(100 gold)"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:123
msgid "Every dwarf dies"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Fighter
#. [side]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:356
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:283
msgid "Dwarves"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Sergeant
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:431
msgid "Zei guards"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Peasant
#. [side], type=Trapper
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:447
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:333
msgid "Merchants"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:474
msgid "Well, it looks like the secret entrance is in a house on the other side."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:478
msgid "And outside more orcs."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:482
msgid "What a surprise."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:490
msgid ""
"Wait! It looks like a few dwarves are getting attacked by the orcs! We need "
"to save them!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:531
msgid ""
"East: Zei\n"
"South: Qyizu, Udxatfe\n"
"North-west: Uvju’s Cross, western tower"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:556
msgid ""
"It looks like the door is blocked by rocks. There's a barrel full of powder "
"next to them. Should I light it up?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:558
msgid "Yes, but be careful not to get hurt."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:578
msgid ""
"The blast was more powerful than I expected. I don't think it is possible to "
"light those barrels up without being hurt by the explosion."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:586
msgid "No, it's too dangerous."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:605
msgid "The door is now cleared. Should I open it?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:607
msgid "Yes, let's open the pass back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:616
msgid "The door is open."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:622
msgid "No, wait a bit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:641
msgid "Well, we were trying to find a way to open this door."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:645
msgid ""
"You must be the reckless farmer my guards talk to me about. I wouldn’t ’ve "
"believed it if I hadn’t seen it with my own eyes."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:649
msgid "Tell me, have you really killed all these orcs?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:653
msgid "Yes, we did."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:657
msgid ""
"Zei is hugely indebted to you, pal. We will do our best to keep the lands "
"you’ve conquered for us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:668
msgid "Here is a little reward for having opened the door."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:672
msgid "Thank you, sir."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:693
msgid ""
"West: Qyizu's mines, Udxatfe\n"
"South-east: Zei"
msgstr ""

#. Giles is speaking in slang
#. Here is the standard equivalent: "How are you doing? If you want to go to Zei, it is pointless. I heard the city was burnt some nights ago."
#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:717
msgid ""
"Wuz crackalackin'. If you wanna git all up in Zei, itz pointless. I heard tha"
" city was burnt some nights ago."
msgstr ""

#. "We are thinking about how we are going to feed the mules until the arrival of our associates."
#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:722
msgid ""
"We is thinin bout tha way we is goin ta feed our mulez until tha arrival of "
"our associates. "
msgstr ""

#. "One mule should be enough now, you see."
#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:727
msgid "To drop a rhyme tha real deal, one mule should be enough now, nahmeean?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:731
msgid "I have no idea what he just said. I think he is trying to sell us a mule."
msgstr ""

#. "Do you want a mule? For 10 gold?"
#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:753
msgid "D-ya want a mule? Fo` 10 gold keep'n it real yo?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:755
msgid "I'm sorry my brave, but we don't need a mule."
msgstr ""

#. "As you wish"
#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:760
msgid "As yo ass wish."
msgstr ""

#. Answer is in slang
#. "Hello, my brave. We would indeed be interested in a mule."
#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:767
msgid "Hello, mah brave. We wizzould indee' be interested 'n a M-to-tha-izzule."
msgstr ""

#. "I am sorry, you don't have enough gold."
#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:782
msgid ""
"I be S-O-Double-Rizzy, bizzy yizzy dizzy have enizzle monizzle (You do not "
"have enough gold)."
msgstr ""

#. [unit], id=Darl'n, type=Bay Horse
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:793
msgid "Darl'n"
msgstr ""

#. "Here it is. What is her name?"
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:802
msgid "Hizzere is. What her nizzle?"
msgstr ""

#. "She is called Darling. I hope she wil suit you."
#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:807
msgid "She be Darl'n. I hizzle she will sizzy you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:845
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:988
msgid "It’s a rough job, but we must live. Besides, we’re not the only ones…"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:855
msgid "I'm sorry we couldn't save more of you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:861
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1004
msgid "What were those orcs doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:865
msgid ""
"They were looking for magical items. And where do you think the magical items"
" that the orcs are stealing go? They end up in the pocket of a Commander "
"Isut."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:869
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1012
msgid "May I be turn into a mule if there is no goblin in all this! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:873
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1016
msgid "You seem to know a lot about what is happening."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:877
msgid ""
"My brother Hufifa must know more but the orcs locked him up down there. I "
"would need your help to free him if you agree."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:881
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, but we need to reach Udxatfe as fast as possible. We don't have "
"the time to enter the mine to look for your brother."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:886
msgid ""
"Don't worry. The way to Udxatfe is through the lower level of the mine. "
"That's where my brother is locked. I will show you the way."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:888
msgid "Sure, we will help you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:903
msgid ""
"Charge! There are some twenty orcs down there to whom we shall teach some "
"manners!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:907
msgid "You can now recruit dwarvish fighters."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:912
msgid "No, it is too dangerous. We'd rather have you to stay here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:916
msgid "You understand nothing! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:920
msgid "We are at war right now. Against whom or against what, nobody knows!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:924
msgid ""
"So, if you think you can get out of it all by yourself, go on, don’t "
"hesitate!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:998
msgid "I'm sorry when couldn't save more of you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1008
msgid ""
"They were looking for magical items. And where do you think go the magical "
"items the orcs are stealing? They end in the pocket of a Commander Isut. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1020
msgid "Hufifa must know more but the orcs locked him up down there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1024
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, but we need to reach Udxatfe as fast as possible. We don't have "
"the time to enter the mine to look for your friend."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1028
msgid ""
"Don't worry. The way to Udxatfe is through the lower level of the mine. "
"That's where Hufifa is locked"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1066
msgid "Well, it looks like we must cross the mines to reach Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1070
msgid "We will try to find and save Hufifa on the way."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1074
msgid "He might have valuable information about what is happening."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1086
msgid "Well, this is where I leave you. See you around."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1113
msgid "The events are too serious that you can continue without a leader."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1123
msgid "I need to go back to Zei and secure Yooradweak's pass."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1127
msgid "For the sake of all of us, I hope you will find Teumiuxe alive."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1151
msgid "You can no longer recruit nor recall Sergeants."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1195
msgid "That's it. The dwarves should be safe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1221
msgid ""
"The dwarves are all dead! How can we imagine saving the country if we can't "
"even save a few persons?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1252
msgid ""
"The dwarves have suffered enough. We won't accept gold from them. Only food "
