#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:566
msgid "Let's recap. Our main mission is still to carry the message to Udxatfe. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:576
msgid ""
"If we can find him, it would be useful to also save Amin's brother, Hufifa, "
"as he probably has information about what is happening."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:580
msgid "This should be our main mission."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:584
msgid ""
"We will do what we can to save your brother, but the fate of the world might "
"be at play here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:588
msgid "Which way is the elevator to the lower level?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:592
msgid "<i>grumpy</i> It's north then west."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:598
msgid ""
"If we can find him, it would be useful to also save Hufifa, as he probably "
"has information about what is happening."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:631
msgid "Giant rats. The mine is swarming with them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:635
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:653
msgid "We tried to get rid of them, but we couldn't find the nest."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:639
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:657
msgid ""
"If we can find and destroy it, it would prevent them from attacking us from "
"behind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:645
msgid "What's this? It looks like a rat, but far bigger."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:649
msgid "Those are giant rats. The mine is swarming with them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:685
msgid ""
"This is the ugliest rat I have ever seen. It must be their king or something "
"like that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:718
msgid "Here are the scorpions I was talking about."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:724
msgid "So those are the famous scorpions Amin told us about."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\12_Mine_Rats.cfg:732
msgid "Come on! Scorpions?! What else?! Flying tigers?!"
msgstr ""

