msgid "Morion with visor of the fox"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2397
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6570
msgid "Plate morion"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2424
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1093
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1217
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6341
msgid "Flexible scale armor"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2425
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6399
msgid "Severe cloth"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2426
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6919
msgid "Rough cloth of vivacity"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2427
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6417
msgid "Cloth of awareness"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2428
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6383
msgid "Organic cloth"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2455
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6850
msgid "Metal targe of the fox"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2456
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6866
msgid "Wooden targe of inversion"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2457
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6894
msgid "Rough wooden shield"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2458
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:6906
msgid "Wooden targe of boldness"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2459
msgid "Intact turtle shield"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2496
msgid "Excuse me. Are you by any chance Owreddoc's sister?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2501
msgid "Yes, I am. How do you know her?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2505
msgid "We come from Zei. The city was attacked."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2509
msgid "Your house was destroyed but your sister is fine. She asked us to tell you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2514
msgid ""
"Thank you for that information all in all mixed: my sister is alive, but our "
"house is nearly destroyed."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2519
msgid ""
"I thank you strangers anyway for bringing me news of my sister. How could I "
"show you my gratitude?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2524
msgid "Hmmmm..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2529
msgid ""
"My father got this ring as a gift after saving the life of a group of "
"minstrels who had fallen into a troll's ambush. It might be time someone "
"worthy wore it; I myself, did nothing to deserve this honor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2534
msgid ""
"I only ask that you to give it to some brave person’s care once you have no "
"more use of it; in memory of my father."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2540
msgid "Here is also some food for your journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2549
msgid "May luck travel with you in your journey"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Siraery
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2563
msgid "A new face. You must be the man who successfully came here from Zei."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2567
msgid "Well, yes."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Siraery
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2571
msgid ""
"I hope you don’t wish to go further than Udxatfe, otherwise your road might "
"be difficult after the eastern swamp, given we drew back the troops."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Mulyn
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2585
msgid ""
"I imagine it must not be too hard to be stationed here. Better stay half a "
"day in the cold than pace up and down the Green Mountains looking for "
"bandits."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2599
msgid ""
"Still another day of severe cold in the mountains. As soon as my wife has "
"sold all those stupid pack mules, we will move to settle somewhere warm."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2613
msgid "Eh, where do you think you are? Shut the door tightly!"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2615
msgid "Sorry, we had no intention of disturbing you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2619
msgid "Then leave! And shut the door tightly!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2638
msgid "Oh, you’re looking for books? To tell the truth, Teoran just lent me one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2642
msgid "He needs it back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2646
msgid "No problem. Here it is. You can thank him for me."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2650
msgid "Sure. We'll bring him back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2668
msgid "I suppose you came to buy me a mule?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2672
msgid "Well not"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2676
msgid "Don’t say anything, I know… "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2680
msgid ""
"You need a docile animal, that can carry heavy burdens, that can travel in "
"the rain, and you can feed when you think about it? That’s it, isn’t it? Of "
"course, but yacks don’t sell!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2700
msgid "I can sell you one for the modest price of 1750 gold."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2702
msgid "I'm sorry but we don't need a mule."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2706
msgid ""
"Do me a favor: buy one of those worthless mules so I can leave this bloody "
"kingdom once and for all."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2712
msgid "Well, I have to say that mules are really practical."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2726
msgid "Of course, they are. But I won't give it to you for free."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2745
msgid "I wonder how practical a yack would be."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2749
msgid "Unless you like yack butter tea, I don't think you'll like them. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Meoddaent
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2771
msgid "Sorry, this sector is forbidden to civilians. Let me mount the guard post."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2791
msgid ""
"My friends, our new mission is to find Teumiuxe the mage. We were told he is "
"a prisoner in the ice caves in the North."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2795
msgid ""
"<i>To himself</i> I hope he is alive. He might know what is happening, and we"
" will need him to save Idaamub. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2823
msgid ""
"It looks like someone build that wall later than the others. I think I could "
"take it down."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2827
msgid "Should I try?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2842
msgid "Well, it was easier than I expected."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2847
msgid "No. This wall was surely built for a good reason."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=18b_Frozen_Cave
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:4
msgid "Frozen Cave"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:43
msgid "Find the road to the ice caves"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:54
msgid "Clean the cave"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Ice Crab
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:184
msgid "Frost Monsters"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:271
msgid "Ery's house should be a bit more north. Let's try to find it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:275
msgid ""
"Once we will have cleaned his cave, we will need to find the road back "
"though."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:281
msgid "Well, there doesn't seem to be a clear path that way."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:285
msgid ""
"It might have been a better idea to stay to the right. But I'm sure we will "
"find the path back soon."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:289
msgid "There is only one way to find out anyway. Let's go."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:320
msgid "I found Ery's house!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:326
msgid "There's a house here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:330
msgid "I wonder who can live there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:357
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:577
msgid "Could this be an Ice Golem?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:361
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:581
msgid ""
"Considering where we are, I think they could have spawned naturally from the "
"ambient ice magic."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:365
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:585
msgid ""
"Or they could have been summoned by the Ice Troll Shamans. I hope the first "
"option is the right one though."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:371
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:591
msgid "What are those things?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:381
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:601
msgid "I think they are Ice Golems."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:385
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:605
msgid ""
"Considering where we are, I think they might have spawned naturally from the "
"ambient ice magic."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:389
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:609
msgid ""
"Or they could have been summoned by the Ice Troll Shamans. I hope the first "
"option is the right one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:414
msgid "There's a chest on the floor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:418
msgid "It looks like it was dragged from the north."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:422
msgid "It's locked."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:433
msgid "The key opened the chest."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:439
msgid "Let's see what's inside."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:457
msgid "There's a key on the floor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:461
msgid "Let's take it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:477
msgid "Brrrr. It's cold in here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:504
msgid ""
"The cave is clean. Now let's continue to the ice caves. The road should be "
"east from the house."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:514
msgid "Let's take a look at the chest before leaving."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:524
msgid "Look what we have here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:556
msgid "I found the road."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:560
msgid "Let's go then."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:573
msgid "This is pointless! Let's go back to the road where we left it."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=18_In_the_Snow
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:4
msgid "In the Snow"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:29
msgid "Go north"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:34
msgid "Find the path to Ery's house"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:250
msgid "My friends, a new adventure awaits us. A cold one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:254
msgid ""
"From what we have heard, the ice cave should be north of here. They are "
"supposed to be full of dangers."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:258
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, this is where we are going. The great mage Teumiuxe is "
"supposedly prisoner in there and we need to free him."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:262
msgid ""
"He should have information on what is happening and his great magic should "
"help us end the troubles."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:272
msgid ""
"We should also pass in front Ery's house. He asked us to clean his basement "
"from frost monsters."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:276
msgid "We'll see if we have the time for that we'll be there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:298
msgid "There is a path here. It seems to lead to a house."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:308
msgid "It must be Ery's house."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:314
msgid "Let's go."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:327
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:365
msgid "Wait for us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:351
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:978
msgid "Let's continue."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Runin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:383
msgid "Snow is tricking me, but I’d swear I have seen things moving around today. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Runin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:387
msgid ""
"If I were you, I’d go back to the inn and eat a good stew ‘til the end of the"
" storm."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Voboger
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:401
msgid "You chose the wrong week to go north.  "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Voboger
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:405
msgid ""
"The road won’t be passable before several month, and the Guardian withdrew "
"all the legionary patrols that were in duty in the underground caves during "
"the attacks. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Voboger
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:409
msgid ""
"There’s no doubt the trolls will have a field day while we’re away. Good luck"
" if you go there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Voboger
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:413
msgid "May Of bless you, pal."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:421
msgid "It was the wrong week to go north."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:425
msgid "We should have stayed in the inn with a good stew."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\18_In_the_Snow.cfg:429
msgid "Now they will only find our frozen corpses in several months."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=19b_Northern_Lights
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:4
msgid "Northern Lights"
msgstr ""

#. [time], id=bright_dawn
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:12
msgid "Bright Dawn"
msgstr ""

#. [time], id=bright_dusk
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:28
msgid "Bright Dusk"
msgstr ""

#. [time], id=first_aurora
#. [time], id=midnight_aurora
#. [time], id=second_aurora
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:38
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:46
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:54
msgid "Aurora Borealis"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:85
msgid "Explore"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:96
msgid "Kill all scorpions"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:308
msgid "I don't see any path."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:312
msgid "Let's explore a bit, and if we don't find a path, we will come back here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:331
msgid "Scorpions? What are scorpions doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:341
msgid "Wait! I recognize this cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:345
msgid "It must be the one of my ancestor Gurdil."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:349
msgid "His ancestor?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:351
msgid "Tell me more."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:355
msgid ""
"<i>starts singing</i>\n"
"One day, my ancestor Gurdil was sent to dig in the forest. There was "
"supposedly mithril there, but if there was, we don't know where it was."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:360
msgid ""
"He made his hut at the border of a dense wood full of wood elves. People "
"eating green sure don't make good neighbors."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:364
msgid ""
"``Go back, you're not welcome'' told him the elves, throwing stones at him. "
"Seeing everything was a complete screw-up, he fled along the river. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:368
msgid ""
"He was taken in by the faeries, blue undines chilling out on the shore. Some "
"rainwater was given to him, he spat everything back into their face! Hahaha!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:372
msgid ""
"Running through the ferns, he arrived near a human village. Of course, they "
"were selling beer. But no human wanted to serve a dwarf."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:376
msgid ""
"Gurdil slaughtered the owner of a tavern with a stool. Then he went back home"
" and never out of the mine again."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:380
msgid "I am not really sure I wanted to know all that."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:385
msgid "Whatever."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:390
msgid "The scorpions must have used this cave as a shelter after it was abandoned."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:396
msgid ""
"Well, anyway, we'd better kill those scorpions so that they don't sting us in"
" the back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:413
msgid "The fog is clearing down here."
msgstr ""

#. [1]
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:427
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:441
msgid "Aurora Borealis?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:431
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:445
msgid ""
"Ah- Aurora Borealis!? At this time of year, at this time of day, in this part"
" of the country, localized entirely above us!?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:459
msgid "Well, clearly, this path is not leading to the ice caves."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:463
msgid "We don't have more time to spend here. Let's head back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:487
msgid "No more scorpions. We did it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19b_Northern_Lights.cfg:491
msgid "Obviously, this path is not leading to the ice caves. Let's go back."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=19_Frozen_Maze
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:4
msgid "Frozen Maze"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:47
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:34
msgid "Defeat the troll leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:57
msgid "Continue north"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:537
msgid "I think I heard noises coming from the East."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:541
msgid ""
"Be prepared. I think we are entering to the core of the ice troll's "
"territory."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:545
msgid "We will probably need to defeat them if we want to continue our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:631
msgid "It's getting foggy out there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:635
msgid "I think I can see a path though."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:639
msgid "Wait! I see two!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:643
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:371
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:467
msgid "Which way should we go?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:649
msgid "Let's go North. That should be the way to the ice caves."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:661
msgid "East"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:665
msgid "Let's go East. That should be the way to the ice caves."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:677
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:433
msgid "Not now"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:681
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:437
msgid "Let's decide later. We are not done here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:698
msgid "It should be easier now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:702
msgid ""
"I don't say that we won't cross the path of some more trolls, but at least "
"the leader is dead."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:710
msgid "So... cold..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:714
msgid "Can't... think..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=20_Ice_Cave
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Cave"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:53
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:32
msgid "Find Teumiuxe"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:64
msgid "Defeat the enemy leader before going east"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Ice Guard LoI
#. [side], type=Ice Swordsman LoI
#. [side], type=Frozen Lich LoI
#. [side], type=Ice Bat LoI
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:108
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:124
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:87
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:76
msgid "Ice Beings"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Ice Troll Shaman LoI
#. [side], type=Ice Bat LoI
#. [side], type=Troll Warrior
#. [side], type=Troll Hero
#. [side], type=Troll Boulderlobber
#. [side], type=Troll Rocklobber
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:517
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:392
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:193
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:78
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:95
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:75
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:183
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:95
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\29_Black_Forest.cfg:92
msgid "Trolls"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:631
msgid "Look! Here it is."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:635
msgid "The Ice Cave. We have finally found it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:639
msgid "Now we need to enter and find Teumiuxe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:649
msgid "Wait a minute. Has this block of ice moved?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:659
msgid "It did it again. This isn't your average everyday block of ice."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:663
msgid "This is, advanced block of ice. It looks a bit like a Swordsman."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:672
msgid "Marvelous!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:676
msgid ""
"This ice cave must have created this being out of ice and magic. It must have"
" imitated the beings that cross it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:680
msgid "I wonder what other kind of creatures we will find in there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:684
msgid "How are you so enthusiast about everything?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:705
msgid "The door opened when I approched."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:716
msgid "Let's see what's in there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=$opener.id
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:775
msgid "I think I just saw this flying piece of ice come out a block of ice."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:784
msgid "You all don't realize! It should not even be possible!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:788
msgid "These ice bats are too heavy to fly. Only magic can make they fly."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:792
msgid "I love this place."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:813
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:838
msgid "It looks like I stepped on some mechanism."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:842
msgid "Look what I found."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:858
msgid ""
"South-west: Udxatfe\n"
"North-east: Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:876
msgid "There is a breeze coming from east."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:880
msgid ""
"If this tunnel goes around the main force, we would be able to either dodge "
"it or attacked it from behind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:916
msgid "I feel a great amount of magic east. This might be Teumiuxe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:926
msgid ""
"It would be good to kill whoever is sending all those ice beings at us before"
" going further. Otherwise, we might have to fight two battles at once."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:934
msgid ""
"I'm glad that we killed the Ice Guard. Otherwise, we might have had to fight "
"two battles at once."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:958
msgid "This cave is bigger than I thought. And still no sign of Teumiuxe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:962
msgid "I did not expect him to be held prisoner right at the entrance, but still."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:968
msgid ""
"This cave is bigger than I thought. But we now have a hint on where Teumiuxe "
"is."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:972
msgid ""
"It's not like we were expecting him to be held prisoner right at the entrance"
" anyway."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:989
msgid "Look other there. There is a treasure in an alcove"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:996
msgid "Maybe it was the treasure gathered by the ice beings."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:1016
msgid "This cave is bigger than I thought. And still now sign of Teumiuxe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:1020
msgid "It is getting too difficult with all those ice beings coming at us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\20_Ice_Cave.cfg:1024
msgid "Let's go back to Udxatfe to ask for help."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=21_Frozen_Chasm
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:4
msgid "Frozen Chasm"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:33
msgid "Defeat who is corrupting the magic"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:43
msgid "Defeat the transformed lich"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:184
msgid ""
"Someone is corrupting the magic for his own deed. Be careful everyone, dark "
"magic is at play."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:190
msgid ""
"I am shivering. But not only from cold. It is as if someone was stepping on "
"my grave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:196
msgid "Be careful everyone. I don't think we will like what is lying further."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:215
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:520
msgid "Aaaaaaahhhh!"
msgstr ""

#. [1]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:219
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:524
msgid "Oh my god! He fell in a crevasse."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lich
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:231
msgid "Fools. I am one with the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lich
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:235
msgid "I will resurrect as one of them and there is nothing you can do about that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Transformed Lich
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:265
msgid "Noooooooooooooooooo..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:269
msgid "Well, looks like the path is cleared. Let's continue."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=22_Ice_Prison
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Prison"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:428
msgid "Teumiuxe"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:458
msgid ""
"I heard a wing flapping. But it does not sound like the ones of these ice "
"bats."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:462
msgid "I wonder what other kind of creature awaits us in this cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:466
msgid ""
"I hope we will find Teumiuxe soon, before being killed by some unexpected ice"
" thing."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:481
msgid ""
"North: Udxatfe \n"
"South: Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:577
msgid "What to say?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:583
msgid ""
"I'm Teumiuxe, the great mage of the 10th legion, third in line for the "
"throne."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:598
msgid "I’ve been hanging for… "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:602
msgid "How much… "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:606
msgid "A bit less than a month."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:610
msgid "Nearly a month, now? This is surprising! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:614
msgid ""
"The power of the ice trolls has really grown. I should have paid more "
"attention to them. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:618
msgid "Damn, I should have seen that coming!"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:629
msgid "Do you know what happened while you were prisoner?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:633
msgid "Tell me."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:642
msgid ""
"Orcs are pillaging the High Arable Lands as well as the surroundings of Zei. "
"Zei has been attacked and pillaged too."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:646
msgid ""
"Someone taught the orcs how to animate the dead and ancient threats are "
"awakening."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:652
msgid ""
"Orcs are pillaging the High Arable Lands as well the surroundings of Zei. Zei"
" has been attacked and pillaged too."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:656
msgid ""
"Someone taught the orcs how to animate the dead and there are human-sized "
"spiders in Uvju's cross."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:662
msgid "Those responsible of this violence are looking for my protection staff. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:666
msgid "Your staff?! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:670
msgid "Yes, this is what they are interested in. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:674
msgid "Is this what they were looking for in Zei?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:678
msgid ""
"Probably. They think it has powers it hasn’t, but it remains a terrible "
"weapon in the wrong hands. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:682
msgid "It must be found back!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:697
msgid ""
"I’m still too weak to go get my protection staff by myself but, if you help "
"me, we should be able to find it together. Will you?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:699
msgid "Of course. How could we refuse your help?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:720
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1882
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1124
msgid "I am sorry, but you seem to be quite a party already."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:737
msgid "This is a good choice. Let’s end the mess I started."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:748
msgid "You'd better go back to safety to Udxatfe. We will find it for you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:752
msgid "Don’t you see what is happening? The fate of the whole kingdom is at stake."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:756
msgid ""
"If you don’t have the guts to help me save all these people, I’ll find "
"someone who do."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:776
msgid ""
"The great mage having succeeded in freeing himself from its ice grave, it is "
"clear now that a maleficent spirit manipulates the forces rampaging the "
"kingdom."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:780
msgid "Our heroes went looking for clues on the hide of the protection staff."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:794
msgid "Still no trace of Teumiuxe. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\22_Ice_Prison.cfg:798
msgid "I'm afraid we have to go back to Udxatfe to announce that we failed... "
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:4
msgid "Abxoowbu's Trading Post"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:58
msgid "Find more information."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:68
msgid "Continue south."
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Cave Bear
#. [side], type=Hell Boar LoI
#. [side], type=Dread Bat
#. [side], type=Direwolf
#. [side], type=Wild Wyvern
#. [side], type=Swamp Lizard
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:112
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\29_Black_Forest.cfg:200
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:184
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:123
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:258
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:119
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\36_Old_Temple_Road.cfg:77
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:96
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:431
msgid "Wildlife"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:373
msgid "Finally! We are out of this freezing cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:377
msgid "Not that it is especially warmer outside."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:386
msgid "I know a merchant that lives a bit south from here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:390
msgid "Well, not really a merchant. Let's call him a trapper."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:394
msgid "He also sells things that he finds in the surrounding woods, or so he says."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:398
msgid ""
"But he has his ways to collect valuable pieces of information. If he is "
"willing to, he might give us some insight on where my staff might be."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:404
msgid "Let's explore a bit the forest. We might find someone knowing something. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:408
msgid ""
"I don't expect to find the location of the staff, but maybe someone will have"
" heard something about a magic artifact. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:414
msgid ""
"The forest looks quite dense. I am afraid we won't be able to get through the"
" woods if the relief is too hilly."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:445
msgid "Argh! I'm burning! The chest was trapped."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:464
msgid "Hello Abxoowbu, how are you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:468
msgid ""
"Hi mage. It has been a long time since I've last seen you there. What are you"
" doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:472
msgid "Have you heard anything about a special staff or a magic artifact?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:476
msgid "Well, I did not think you could fall so low. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:482
msgid ""
"Excuse me, my brave. Would you happen to have heard anything about a special "
"staff or a magic artifact?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:486
msgid "Who are YOU? One more minion of this nasty little goblin? "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:492
msgid ""
"Tell this greenish guttersnipe that I don’t have his precious staff and never"
" had it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:496
msgid ""
"I don’t deal exotic items and even if I had had such a staff, there is no way"
" I would go deep into the eastern swamp to sell it to a mother of stranger."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:500
msgid "Hurry up telling me what you want before I kick your behind back to the snow."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:504
msgid "Well at least we got some information."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Csia,Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:513
msgid "Hmmm... the Eastern Swamp. This is south."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Csia,Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:517
msgid "This means we have to cross Oa's gallery."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Csia,Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:521
