#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1401
msgid "I know this cave. This is Oa's gallery."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1405
msgid ""
"It is full of trolls and saurians. They will not be very happy to see us on "
"their territory. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1409
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, this is the shortest way to the eastern swamp, and this is "
"where my staff seems to be."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1415
msgid ""
"I don't like the look of this cave. I'm sure it is full of deadly creatures, "
"lurking in the dark.  "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1419
msgid "Unfortunately, it seems to be the only way to continue our travel."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1423
msgid "We need to reach the eastern swamp and recover Teumiuxe's staff."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:27
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:29
msgid "Cross the cave"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:38
msgid "Stop the aggressive fishes before leaving"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Sea Serpent
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:83
msgid "Fishes"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Saurian Ambusher
#. [side], type=Water Serpent
#. [side], type=Saurian Flanker
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:101
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:98
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:94
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:77
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:162
msgid "Saurians"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:357
msgid ""
"I didn't expect so much water in this cave. I can see it streaming down the "
"walls and I can hear droplets falling on the ground."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:361
msgid "This cave is really special you know."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:365
msgid ""
"It was formed a long time ago, when a spell went entropic made an underwater "
"cave rise above the ground."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:369
msgid "Since then, the cave still contain water, but also a lot of magic."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Lujeje
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:373
msgid "It is even said that you can meet sea creatures in it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:377
msgid "Alright everyone! Try not to slip."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:381
msgid ""
"The exit should be south. But we will probably have to fight the saurians for"
" that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:400
msgid "I know there is a lot of water here, but I did not expect to see a fish."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:405
msgid ""
"They seem aggressive. I am afraid we will have to fight them on top of the "
"saurians."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:418
msgid ""
"This horror was probably the mother of the fishes. We should have some peace "
"now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:438
msgid ""
"Crossing this cave is difficult enough with all those saurians, and now we "
"had to fight fishes on top of it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:442
msgid ""
"I don't know how long this cave is, but I hope the situation will be better "
"on the other side of it. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:446
msgid "Unfortunately, with what we heard in Udxatfe, I am afraid it won't be."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:479
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the fishes here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:487
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the saurians here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:499
msgid ""
"I don't think we will be able to pass through both the saurians and the "
"fishes."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\24_Deep_Water.cfg:503
msgid "We need to find another way."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=25_Troll_Cave
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:4
msgid "Troll Cave"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Bay Horse
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:423
msgid "Horse"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:505
msgid "Wait! I recognize this noise."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:509
msgid ""
"It sounds exactly like the ice troll leader we defeated before entering the "
"ice cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:513
msgid "But it should be too warm here for the ice trolls?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:517
msgid ""
"You are unfortunately right. This cave is full of trolls. Not the ice "
"version, but the normal ones."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:521
msgid ""
"When I withdrew all the legionary patrols that were in duty in the "
"underground caves during the attacks, there’s no doubt the trolls had a field"
" day while they were away."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:525
msgid ""
"We need to kill the troll leader. That should disorganize them enough that we"
" can easily take back control of the cave later."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:529
msgid "I am afraid we will have to fight those trolls to continue our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:544
msgid ""
"South: Black Forest\n"
"North: Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:568
msgid ""
"I do not like leaving those trolls roaming the path behind us, but we have a "
"more important mission than dealing with them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:595
msgid ""
"Now that we dealt with those trolls, the traffic should be able to start "
"again from Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:599
msgid "Let's try to find the exit of this cave... and the staff."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:613
msgid "First saurians, then fishes and now trolls."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:617
msgid "That's too much for us. We are not legionaries."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:630
msgid "Hey there, pal. Don't worry, you're safe now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:634
msgid "That's quite a bad situation you got into. Want to come with us?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:664
msgid "There's a horse here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:668
msgid "What is it doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:672
msgid "Maybe it fled from fear and got stuck here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\25_Troll_Cave.cfg:676
msgid "It will not leave long alone here. Maybe we could try to get to it."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=26b_Troll_Fort
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:4
msgid "Troll Fort"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:53
msgid "Clean the fort"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:271
msgid "Those ruins look weird. They don't look like something trolls would build."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:281
msgid ""
"They are indeed no troll ruins. This is where the legionary patrols were "
"living in the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:285
msgid ""
"The fort is a bit north.\n"
"It would be good to flush them out of it. Legionaries would then have an "
"easier time coming here to patrol again."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:292
msgid ""
"There seems to be some kind of fort further north. I imagine the path goes "
"through it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:456
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:687
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:794
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1029
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1136
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1615
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1707
msgid "There is a lever on the floor. Should I pull it down?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:481
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:704
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:819
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1046
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1161
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1667
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1736
msgid "There is a lever on the floor. Should I pull it up?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1206
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1273
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1340
msgid "There is a chest. Should I open it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1220
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1287
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1354
msgid "It is empty."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1236
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1303
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1370
msgid "Argh! The chest was trapped."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1244
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1311
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1378
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:445
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:462
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:479
#: .\utils\macros.cfg:324
msgid "There is something in the chest."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1251
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1318
msgid "No, it might be trapped."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1420
msgid ""
"I think there are no more trolls in there. We can go back to the crossing and"
" take the other path to the exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1448
msgid ""
"We already spent too much time here. We do not have enough time to clean the "
"whole fort.\n"
"Let's go."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1461
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1495
msgid ""
"We already spent too much time here. I don't think the exit is this way.\n"
"Let's go back to the crossing and take the other road."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1482
msgid ""
"I think there are no more trolls in there. \n"
"Let's go back to the crossing and take the other path to the exit."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=26_Echo_Chamber
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:4
msgid "Echo Chamber"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:26
msgid "Defeat enemy leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:31
msgid "Defeat all enemies"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:324
msgid ""
"It sounds like there are more trolls ahead. They must be in a huge room by "
"the echo."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:328
msgid "Anyway, we need to advance. I am sure the exit is not far."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:340
msgid "Oh, I understand the echo now. The chamber is not huge, it is really deep."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:353
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:463
msgid "The road splits here. We can go north or south."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:364
msgid ""
"The road north leads to the legionaries' fort. It is a dead end but I am "
"afraid it is now full of trolls. \n"
"The road south continues to the exit of the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:383
msgid "We should clean the fort before leaving."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:389
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:473
msgid "Let's go North. That should be the way out."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:413
msgid "We have no time to clean the fort. Our mission is too urgent."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:419
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:489
msgid "Let's go South. That should be the way out."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:457
msgid "It is so quiet now. I think this was the last one."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=27_Saurian_Pond
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Pond"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:28
msgid "Defeat the saurian leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:33
msgid "Defeat all leaders"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Purple Crystal LoI
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:164
msgid "Crystals"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:295
msgid ""
"I am a bit worried about letting those trolls behind us. I hope they will not"
" come to stab us in the back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:305
msgid ""
"I'm afraid we don't have time to worry now. We are now entering the saurian "
"territory."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:309
msgid "They might not be as impressive as trolls, but they are fierce warriors."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:315
msgid ""
"We do not have time to worry though. We must find the exit of this cave and "
"the protection staff."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:324
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:339
msgid "It should be a bit better now that we have killed the troll leaders."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Csia,Lujeje,Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:328
msgid ""
"I'm however afraid that we might only have killed some of them. There might "
"still be more hidden in the cave we left."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Csia,Lujeje,Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:332
msgid ""
"However, I do not think this is a good time to think about that. Even if we "
"had killed all trolls in this cave, there are still others enemies awaiting "
"us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Csia,Lujeje,Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:343
msgid "This is unfortunately not how it works."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Csia,Lujeje,Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:347
msgid ""
"There is now an empty spot in the hierarchy of the cave. The other creatures "
"are going to fight to find out which will take their place."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Csia,Lujeje,Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:351
msgid "Be prepared to fight aggressive creatures."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:355
msgid "Wait, you mean we should have left the trolls live."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe,Csia,Lujeje,Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:359
msgid ""
"No, we had to deal with them. But now we need to deal with the other "
"creatures. Otherwise, the cave will be even more dangerous in the following "
"weeks, the time needed for things to calm down."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:378
msgid "That's one huge crystal."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:382
msgid ""
"It looks like it is controlling the other ones. Maybe destroying it would "
"disturb the others for a while."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:401
msgid "That was a hard fight, but I think we cleaned the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:405
msgid "It even looks like this one was guardian a treasure."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:409
msgid ""
"Not that we are doing that for gold, but we might need it for our journey. "
"Take it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:413
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:443
msgid ""
"I'm glad we finally found the exit. I would not have spent another day in "
"that cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:439
msgid ""
"It is a mess here with all those creatures fighting for their small part of "
"this cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:447
msgid ""
"Let's leave before they decide that we are more interesting than protecting "
"their territory."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:459
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:558
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\29_Black_Forest.cfg:598
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:662
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1678
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:472
msgid ""
"There are too many creatures there. Let's go back and try to find another way"
" through the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:489
msgid ""
"North-West: Black Forest\n"
"South-East: Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=28_Travelers
#. [side], type=Duelist
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:4
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:299
msgid "Travelers"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:41
msgid "Find the camp fire."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:51
msgid "Leave south."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:406
msgid "Finally, back outside. I was getting tired of the trolls."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:416
msgid ""
"Well, now that you mention it, the legion was not only controlling the trolls"
" INSIDE Oa's gallery. It was also preventing them from going OUTSIDE Oa's "
"gallery."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:420
msgid ""
"So, what you are telling me is that we should expect more trolls out here, "
"shouldn't we?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:424
msgid "I'm afraid so."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:428
msgid "What did I do to deserve this?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia,Lujeje,Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:434
msgid "I'm sorry to be a bummer, but it looks like there are trolls outside too."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:438
msgid "Oh, come on!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:444
msgid "Wait, don't you smell smoke?"
msgstr ""

#. [1]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:448
msgid "Could be a distress fire... or a barbecue."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:452
msgid "A distress barbecue?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:456
msgid ""
"Anyway, we need to find out if it comes from friends or foes, if it is good "
"or bad news."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:460
msgid "I sure hope it's a barbecue."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:474
msgid "Who goez there? Friend or foe?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:478
msgid "I don't know, who are you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:482
msgid ""
"What do you mean you don't know? Are you ztupid or are you trying to get "
"killed?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:486
msgid "We are travellerz? What about you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:490
msgid ""
"We are a party on a mission for the kingdom of Idaamub. But it is a secret "
"mission."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:494
msgid "Then you're friendz. You might actually even be able to help uz."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:498
msgid ""
"You can get zome rezt in our camp. We could even do some buzinezz if you have"
" zome money or thingz to zell."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:502
msgid "We smelled the smoke of your fire from far away. Was it a distress signal?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:506
msgid "No, we're juzt grilling some meat."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:510
msgid "I knew it!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:514
msgid ""
"Well, it looks like we found the source of the smell. They don't seem to be "
"in immediate trouble, so I think we can continue as soon as we want."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:542
msgid ""
"My friends, it seems our mission is getting more dangerous. From what we "
"learnt here, we won't have to face only the goblins to get the staff back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:546
msgid "Anyway, this cannot stop us, as the destiny of Idaamub is in our hands."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:568
msgid "Wait a minute. We still need to find where this smell comes from."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Rhadoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:585
msgid "It muzt have been written zomewhere that our life will only be zuffering."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Rhadoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:593
msgid ""
"The men of our camp are buzy anzwering the bravado of the harmlezz bandits, "
"but I zee emerging a danger far greater than those banditz. Be careful if you"
" go in the zwamp."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:597
msgid "What is the problem?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Rhadoc
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:601
msgid ""
"During more than a month, my zizterz and I had nightmarez in which we were "
"zeeing an huge army of zoullezz goblinz. There were bowing down before a huge"
" black zymbol of power which waz getting bigger and bigger, fulled by the "
"revenge and the hatred of the abyzz’ demonz. I fear the powerluzt of the "
"goblins cauzez an invazion of the forcez of evil."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ritharry
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:615
msgid ""
"We are indeed going through a trial. It began with the rapt of our zizter "
"Bta, and now the banditz are threatening to kill uz."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fdi
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:629
msgid "Evil-eyed creaturez… came… and took my Bta."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:633
msgid "What kind of creatures?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fdi
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:637
msgid ""
"They look like the horrible Ockz from the legendz… but how could it be "
"pozzible? The Ockz were killed… slaughtered three hundred yearz ago by the "
"first king of your kingdom. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fdi
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:641
msgid ""
"But I am confident my daughter will give them a hard time. She is a… "
"Traveler."
msgstr ""

