"The good news is that we found the goblins, which means the staff is "
"hopefully not far."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1581
msgid ""
"The bad news is that we also found whatever that weird thing up there was. "
"I'm afraid it might not be a one-of-a-kind."
