#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1587
msgid "There seems to be a corridor behind."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1592
msgid "No, we don't have the tools for that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1647
msgid "A second lever appear on the floor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1653
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1673
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1742
msgid "It's blocked."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1724
msgid "Part of the opposite wall slid down."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1768
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\38_Isut.cfg:559
msgid "What's that?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1783
msgid "Goblin contraption, that's what it's. Let me grab my hammer."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1787
msgid "Wait! What's the purpose of it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1791
msgid "Who cares? I say we remove it for the undersurface of the earth."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1795
msgid "Amin..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1799
msgid ""
"Ok, ok. It looks like a giant steam engine. And it looks like it is running. "
"I have no idea what it powers though."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1803
msgid "What's a steam engine?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1807
msgid ""
"A device that produces mechanical energy with water and fire. But I would in "
"no way trust one of goblin fabrication, it could explode anytime, killing "
"everyone in the tunnels."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1811
msgid "But you understand how it works, don't you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1815
msgid ""
"I know how a normal one works, not the weird goblin death machines. But I can"
" have a look if you want. It will not be said that a dwarf will fail to "
"understand how an engine works, be it a goblin one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1819
msgid "Please do."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1841
msgid ""
"I have never seen such a terrible job at making an engine. I have no idea how"
" it has not exploded yet. I assume the numerous leaks prevent the pressure "
"from rising high enough to do so.\n"
"Anyway, if you really want to make it do whatever it is supposed to, you "
"should turn the four big wheel that are placed on each side of the engine. "
"Then Of bless us for what will happen."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1852
msgid ""
"It looks a bit like the goblin engines. I wonder what it does and how it "
"ended up here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1856
msgid "It looks like there some kind of big wheel on each side."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1860
msgid "Maybe something will happen if we turn each of them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1886
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1922
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1958
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1994
msgid "There is a huge wheel. Should I turn it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2024
msgid "Should we go?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2056
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2335
msgid "Yes, we are wasting our time here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2060
msgid "Let's go back and take the main road instead."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2100
msgid "No, I am sure there is another exit."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2135
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2559
msgid "Yes, this exit should bring us closer to our goal."
msgstr ""

#. [unit], id=trader, type=Rogue
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2183
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2391
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2611
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2815
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:664
msgid "Oddaty, the Scavenger"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2252
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2692
msgid "Well, it looks like I was wrong, this was not a shortcut."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2256
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2696
msgid ""
"I have been misled by all the tunnels and caves we have used as shortcut or "
"detour since the beginning of our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2260
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2700
msgid "Let's continue on the main road instead."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2339
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2956
msgid "There is no sign of the treasure hunters and our mission is urgent."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2343
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2962
msgid "Let's go back and continue down the old temple road."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2472
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2704
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2896
msgid "Back already? Have you found the treasure hunters?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2476
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2708
msgid ""
"I'm sorry but we've seen no sign of that and we have to time to look longer "
"after then."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2480
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2712
msgid ""
"I understand. Still, I hope we will find out what happened to them. In these "
"difficult times, it would be regrettable to lose their... support."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2484
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2716
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2919
msgid "Goodbye. Now, let's continue our journey down the old temple road."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2524
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2756
msgid "No, we have not found the treasure hunters yet."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2563
msgid ""
"There is no sign of the treasure hunters and our mission is too urgent to "
"waste more time here."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2767
msgid "Yes, we should go report to Oboavlidlu."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2900
msgid "I'm sorry but they are dead."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2904
msgid "You found them dead? That’s marvelous!... Hmm... It is a bit unfortunate."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2908
msgid ""
"I knew they were not the kind to leave without saying goodbye. Please take "
"this modest sum in return for your help."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2915
msgid ""
"Oddaty and I will have to go there without delay to make sure to provide a..."
" hmm... decent burial to those poor lads."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2946
msgid "We are wasting our time here."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=35_Scavengers_Trading_Post
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:4
msgid "Scavenger's Trading Post"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:48
msgid "Find out where you are"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:58
msgid "Go down the old temple road to Oof's fortress."
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Foul Dark Wose LoI
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:100
msgid "Dark Woses"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:720
msgid ""
"The elevator leads us here. I have no idea where we are. I hope we are no too"
" far from an exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:724
msgid ""
"It looks like there are some machines further, but they don't seem to move. "
"They probably got disabled with the rest of the complex."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:733
msgid "I gonna smash'em."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:798
msgid "There seem to be a lever there. I gonna pull it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:815
msgid "A huge rock slid and opened a hole in the wall. It seems I found the exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:835
msgid "Pull it please."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:851
msgid "A huge rock slid and opened a hole in the wall."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:855
msgid "It seems we found the exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:865
msgid "Wait, those are legionaries. Let me talk to them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:889
msgid "Legionary, report!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:893
msgid "The Great Mage!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:897
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:967
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1029
msgid "By Of’s shield, is the Guardian sending you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:901
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:971
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1033
msgid ""
"Actually, we are on a mission for the kingdom, but we might be of mutual "
"help."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:905
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:975
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1037
msgid "Tell me, where are we and what are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:909
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:979
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1041
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, we are in the middle of nowhere. Our detachment left Oof's "
"fortress to try to get emergency reinforcement from Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:913
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:983
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1045
msgid ""
"Four days ago, a necromancer with terrible powers by the name of Isut "
"appeared and fell onto us, flanked by undead and Dunefolk. The Dunefolk "
"outnumbering us, they blocked access to Idaamub’s castle from the east and we"
" got blocked from both sides."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:917
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:987
msgid "That is terrible news."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:921
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:991
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1053
msgid ""
"The six of us left by the old temple road to dodge Isut, but we fell onto one"
" of his tentacle guardians, which did not spare us. We both took refuge here,"
" but it is impossible to bring reinforcement from the legion to captain "
"Soimaql on time."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:925
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:995
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1057
msgid "We might be able to do something about that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:929
msgid ""
"I know who you are, I think you should be a match for Isut. You could give my"
" comrades the boost they need to stop this monster before he kills us all."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:933
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1003
msgid "Our course of action is clear."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:937
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1007
msgid ""
"We need to go down the old temple road to reach Oof's fortress and free it "
"from Isut."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:941
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1011
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1069
msgid "We will then join Idaamub's castle to help break the Dunefolk siege."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:945
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1015
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1073
msgid "Once it is done, we will be able to deliver our message to the king."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:949
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1019
msgid "Stay here to heal your wounds. You will be of no help like that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:953
msgid "Sir, yes, Sir!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:963
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1025
msgid "Excuse me, sir."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:999
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1061
msgid ""
"I don’t know who you are, but if you’re as competent as you look like, I "
"think you should be a match for Isut. You could give my comrades the boost "
"they need to stop this monster before he kills us all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1049
msgid "That's terrible news."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1065
msgid ""
"Well, looks like we need to go down the old temple road to reach Oof's "
"fortress and free it from Isut."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Alealyan
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1096
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\37_Old_Temple.cfg:726
msgid ""
"Those tentacles, those teeth… those flickering lights… and all those dead… "
"why so many dead?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1100
msgid "Looks like he lost his mind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1114
msgid ""
"Milord Oddaty and I supplied a group of treasure hunters that were examining "
"the flooded tunnels west. Maybe you are also going in that direction?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1118
msgid "I'm sorry but we aren't."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1122
msgid "They have not come for several days. They never talked about leaving."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1126
msgid ""
"It is always displeasing to lose regular customers, especially when you do "
"not know where they went. If by chance you meet them, tell them we appreciate"
" doing business with them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1130
msgid ""
"Well, if we happen to meet them, we will tell them you are looking forward "
"seeing them again."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1134
msgid ""
"And if it happens that they… hmm… closed their account, come back to tell us "
"where they are."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1138
msgid ""
"I am sorry, but, even if we were to visit those tunnels, I do not think we "
"would have the time to come back to you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1142
msgid ""
"You would not regret it, I promise. In these difficult times, it would be "
"regrettable to lose their… support."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1146
msgid ""
"Were I to learn that you go into the tunnels, I would wait for you at their "
"entrance; that way you will not have to come back here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1162
msgid ""
"Come in, come in! Hmm… you do not seem move in the best circles, but one "
"should never under-estimate the lower classes…"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1166
msgid ""
"My assistant and I have found these items on a group of mages on the temple "
"road. Some of these items might interest you, but we have not yet got them "
"rid of their… unpleasant smell."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1170
msgid "But it should not disturb someone like you, should it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1211
msgid "What can Oddaty the Scavenger do for you today?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1454
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:13918
msgid "Avenging blade-staff of revival"
msgstr ""

