#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:633
msgid ""
"Of be blessed, you came up at the right time. I doubt we would have been able"
" to defend the fort one more day without you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:647
msgid ""
"If you succeed in defeating Isut's army, you should be able to reach without "
"any difficulty the Hall of Skulls. The captain has sent there a detachment of"
" soldiers to search for a woman who he thinks has been captured, but they "
"should be back already now."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:661
